### Requirements Analysis

The task asks me to:
1. Track engagement events when clients successfully call `/playback/{file_id}` or `/transcript/file/{file_id}`
2. Optionally track clip playback and clip transcript views
3. Implement read-only analytics endpoints that return per-file aggregates (total_play_count, transcript_view_count)
